The time derivative of Euler angle rotations for the twelve sequences are:

1. XYX: \begin{equation}
\begin{bmatrix}
\dot{\phi}\\
\dot{\theta}\\
\dot{\psi}
\end{bmatrix}
= 
\begin{bmatrix}
\dot{\phi}\\
\dot{\theta}\cos\phi\\
\dot{\theta}\sin\phi
\end{bmatrix}
\end{equation}
