where q = [phi, theta, psi] and the sequence of rotations is roll about x, pitch about y, and then yaw about z.

18. ZXY Sequence:
B(q) = [ cos(theta)*cos(psi)-sin(phi)*sin(psi)*sin(theta)  cos(psi)*sin(theta)+cos(theta)*sin(phi)*sin(psi)  -cos(phi)*sin(theta);
